            <title>[SOLR-9772] FieldSortValues should reuse comparator and only invalidate leafComparator</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9772</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In QueryComponent.doFieldSortValues when there are multiple leafs a comparator and leafComparator is made for each document instead of creating a common comparator and making as different leafs are visited.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
