&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9772&quot; title=&quot;FieldSortValues should reuse comparator and only invalidate leafComparator&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-9772&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-9772&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; FieldSortValues should reuse comparator and only invalidate leafComparator&lt;/p&gt;

